item.description:
I am a Computational Biology Research Scientist at UCSF HDFC Cancer Center. Additionally, I hold Adjunct Research Scientist position at the Nepal Applied Mathematics & Informatics Institute for Research (NAAMII), where I am leading the Computational Genomics Laboratory. [My Bio]

My main interest lies in understanding cancer progression and treatment resistance through the development and application of computational genomics approaches.

I am actively looking for academic faculty position.
